{"tid":1788570,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[反送中歌曲］ 如戴著面具去掩飾倦容 迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆","createTime":"2019-12-18T18:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T19:48:14.000Z","uid":42141,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe8363be8799d2095e43842703831336481c40c","tid":1788570,"uid":42141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:50:13.000Z","msg":"今晚心情唔好<br />\n聽到許庭鏗嘅面具<br />\n<br />\n發覺其實都幾貼近班學生出嚟發夢<br />\n又辛苦又攰都話自己無事<br />\n<br />\n想睇下有冇巴絲可以用呢首歌剪條片，拎返個共鳴<br />\n自己唔爭氣<br />\n又唔識呢方面嘅嘢<br />\n跪求大家幫手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/brw2aEgkw4I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fbrw2aEgkw4I&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6s2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=db7f6d37\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/brw2aEgkw4I</a><br />\n<br />\n發過要發的夢 但熱烈漸覺冰凍<br />\n跌過痛過便會懂<br />\n誰在作弄 沉默背後也想發狂<br />\n很想找一剎來放縱 斗膽一次如反恐<br />\n也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝<br />\n衝出困局 形象似義勇軍般英勇<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如戴著面具去掩飾倦容<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 懷着理想那怕痛</span><br />\n<br />\n也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝<br />\n衝出困局 形象似義勇軍般英勇<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如戴著面具去掩飾倦容<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 忘卻世間的縳束</span><br />\n<br />\n誰明白像和你也許重逢<br />\n遺憾太多卻不能倒流的鐘<br />\n如琴聲的哀號 連結他都哭訴<br />\n誰明白我初衷 煩躁也是個夢 但我真的痛"},{"pid":"6a3267f22c3235ac02de1fdaa345b517a26ddbc5","tid":1788570,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6s2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=b9a85e24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6s2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=8c1776eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a><br />\n<br />\n請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca10f634984d2f0baf4b994d7e31ebf5e3b03c59","tid":1788570,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T19:02:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">形象似義勇軍般英勇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3cf1e6a713ff3af728584d926da0d695ba439b","tid":1788570,"uid":42141,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca10f634984d2f0baf4b994d7e31ebf5e3b03c59","tid":1788570,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T19:02:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">形象似義勇軍般英勇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T19:03:27.000Z","msg":"咁多句你唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6f4d5864624a87dff9605b11a66944e2aa6f1d","tid":1788570,"uid":42141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T19:14:40.000Z","msg":"如果係咁<br />\n我推多兩下就算"},{"pid":"616e11179c8b4b5fa3fe83e2af799a106defc630","tid":1788570,"uid":42141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T19:23:03.000Z","msg":"推埋呢次"},{"pid":"51cedf3e37e9cf0430ec0d74a2ff8cca6428b146","tid":1788570,"uid":307619,"